,"quote":{"pid":"134ac63430d81d86cda61316e2b5b054df783bb1","tid":2249444,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"唔用機點計log啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"你代入去試下就知 會變成(log3/log5 - log3/log5 -2)^5所以其實無得禁機無問題 basic maths"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"理解唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"好易理解 <br />\n首先,<br />\n25^(3m) = 3<br />\nLog (25^(3m)) = log 3<br />\n3m log 25 = log 3 <br />\nm = (log 3)/(3 log 25) = (log 3)/(6 log 5)<br />\n然後第二part, <br />\n5^(7n) = 1/3<br />\nLog (5^(7n)) = log (1/3)<br />\n7n log 5 = - log 3<br />\nn = - (log 3)/(7 log 5)<br />\n最後代返入去條式到,<br />\n(6m + 7n - 2)^5 <br />\n= ( 6(log 3)/( 6 log 5) + 7(- (log 3)/(7 log 5)) -2)^5<br />\n= ( (log 3)/(log 5) - (log 3)/(log 5) - 2)^5<br />\n= (-2)^5<br />\n= -32"},{"pid":"beccacb2777a6406dec3a14e18eb8dfbfa866473","tid":2249444,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26d1ecaed4e0f1190a394b423c6991f9a4a880b","tid":2249444,"uid":235754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"128f8dfd5bb62650ceed40a11d8f66dd99369744","tid":2249444,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77a3a0865170f5df84a7a7bcc6190c2a102a6f20","tid":2249444,"uid":235754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"你代入去試下就知 會變成(log3/log5 - log3/log5 -2)^5所以其實無得禁機無問題 basic maths"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"理解唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"好易理解 <br />\n首先,<br />\n25^(3m) = 3<br />\nLog (25^(3m)) = log 3<br />\n3m log 25 = log 3 <br />\nm = (log 3)/(3 log 25) = (log 3)/(6 log 5)<br />\n然後第二part, <br />\n5^(7n) = 1/3<br />\nLog (5^(7n)) = log (1/3)<br />\n7n log 5 = - log 3<br />\nn = - (log 3)/(7 log 5)<br />\n最後代返入去條式到,<br />\n(6m + 7n - 2)^5 <br />\n= ( 6(log 3)/( 6 log 5) + 7(- (log 3)/(7 log 5)) -2)^5<br />\n= ( (log 3)/(log 5) - (log 3)/(log 5) - 2)^5<br />\n= (-2)^5<br />\n= -32"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"咁我明喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係依家小一要計埋啲咁嘅嘢？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a2f0c0f7ed8ad9d64d025619d4d5e1bdf672b5","tid":2249444,"uid":99827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beccacb2777a6406dec3a14e18eb8dfbfa866473","tid":2249444,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26d1ecaed4e0f1190a394b423c6991f9a4a880b","tid":2249444,"uid":235754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"128f8dfd5bb62650ceed40a11d8f66dd99369744","tid":2249444,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"理解唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"好易理解 <br />\n首先,<br />\n25^(3m) = 3<br />\nLog (25^(3m)) = log 3<br />\n3m log 25 = log 3 <br />\nm = (log 3)/(3 log 25) = (log 3)/(6 log 5)<br />\n然後第二part, <br />\n5^(7n) = 1/3<br />\nLog (5^(7n)) = log (1/3)<br />\n7n log 5 = - log 3<br />\nn = - (log 3)/(7 log 5)<br />\n最後代返入去條式到,<br />\n(6m + 7n - 2)^5 <br />\n= ( 6(log 3)/( 6 log 5) + 7(- (log 3)/(7 log 5)) -2)^5<br />\n= ( (log 3)/(log 5) - (log 3)/(log 5) - 2)^5<br />\n= (-2)^5<br />\n= -32"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"咁我明喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係依家小一要計埋啲咁嘅嘢？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:36:10.000Z","msg":"內文係中一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c1670f458df0e4e91b0133ccf5e34489050bde","tid":2249444,"uid":121076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,